'''BuzzFeed'''是一間美國的網路新聞媒體公司，由{{tsl|en|Jonah Peretti|喬納·派瑞提}}於2006年在紐約市成立。公司最初是一間研究網路熱門話題的實驗室（{{lang|en|viral lab}}），如今已成為全球性的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/media/entertainment/media/buzzfeed-gets-50-mn-cash-infusion-to-set-up-operations-in-india/articleshow/40120844.cms|title=BuzzFeed gets $50 mn cash infusion, to set up operations in India|work=The Economic Times|accessdate=2015-05-10|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816052341/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/media/entertainment/media/buzzfeed-gets-50-mn-cash-infusion-to-set-up-operations-in-india/articleshow/40120844.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>媒體和科技公司，提供包括政治、手工藝、動物和商業等主題的新聞內容。2011年下半，《[[Politico|Politico]]》雜誌的{{tsl|en|Ben_Smith_(journalist)||班·史密斯}}受聘為{{lang|en|BuzzFeed}}的總編輯，希望能藉此增加較嚴肅之新聞和長篇報導內容<ref>{{cite web|last=Stelter|first=Brian|url=http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/12/12/buzzfeed-adds-politico-writer/|title=BuzzFeed Adds Politico Writer|publisher=Mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com|date=2011-12-12|accessdate=2012-01-21|archive-date=2011-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111212155914/http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/12/12/buzzfeed-adds-politico-writer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
